<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN" "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd">
<plist version="1.0">
<dict>
	<key>CFBundleDevelopmentRegion</key>
	<string>$(DEVELOPMENT_LANGUAGE)</string>
	<key>CFBundleDisplayName</key>
	<string>MarkEn IoT</string>
	<key>CFBundleExecutable</key>
	<string>$(EXECUTABLE_NAME)</string>
	<key>CFBundleIdentifier</key>
	<string>$(PRODUCT_BUNDLE_IDENTIFIER)</string>
	<key>CFBundleInfoDictionaryVersion</key>
	<string>6.0</string>
	<key>CFBundleName</key>
	<string>cold_chain_monitor</string>
	<key>CFBundlePackageType</key>
	<string>APPL</string>
	<key>CFBundleShortVersionString</key>
	<string>$(FLUTTER_BUILD_NAME)</string>
	<key>CFBundleSignature</key>
	<string>????</string>
	<key>CFBundleVersion</key>
	<string>$(FLUTTER_BUILD_NUMBER)</string>
	<key>LSRequiresIPhoneOS</key>
	<true/>

	<!-- ✅ Camera — required for QR scanner -->
	<key>NSCameraUsageDescription</key>
	<string>Camera access is required to scan QR codes for device registration.</string>

	<!-- ✅ Photo Library — required for image picker -->
	<key>NSPhotoLibraryUsageDescription</key>
	<string>Photo library access is required to select QR code images for device registration.</string>

	<!-- ✅ Photo Library Add — required for saving images -->
	<key>NSPhotoLibraryAddUsageDescription</key>
	<string>Permission required to save images to your photo library.</string>

	<!-- ✅ Notifications — required for alerts -->
	<key>NSUserNotificationsUsageDescription</key>
	<string>Notifications are used to alert you when equipment temperature goes out of safe range.</string>

	<!-- ✅ Local Network — required for IoT device communication -->
	<key>NSLocalNetworkUsageDescription</key>
	<string>Local network access is required to communicate with hospital equipment.</string>

	<!-- ✅ Google Sign-In URL scheme -->
	<key>CFBundleURLTypes</key>
	<array>
		<dict>
			<key>CFBundleTypeRole</key>
			<string>Editor</string>
			<key>CFBundleURLSchemes</key>
			<array>
				<!-- Replace with your REVERSED_CLIENT_ID from GoogleService-Info.plist -->
				<string>com.googleusercontent.apps.653168096175-0ebb60n39if5jb7vmhmch980ec6hsfms</string>
			</array>
		</dict>
	</array>

	<key>UILaunchStoryboardName</key>
	<string>LaunchScreen</string>
	<key>UIMainStoryboardFile</key>
	<string>Main</string>
	<key>UISupportedInterfaceOrientations</key>
	<array>
		<string>UIInterfaceOrientationPortrait</string>
		<string>UIInterfaceOrientationLandscapeLeft</string>
		<string>UIInterfaceOrientationLandscapeRight</string>
	</array>
	<key>UISupportedInterfaceOrientations~ipad</key>
	<array>
		<string>UIInterfaceOrientationPortrait</string>
		<string>UIInterfaceOrientationPortraitUpsideDown</string>
		<string>UIInterfaceOrientationLandscapeLeft</string>
		<string>UIInterfaceOrientationLandscapeRight</string>
	</array>
	<key>CADisableMinimumFrameDurationOnPhone</key>
	<true/>
	<key>UIApplicationSupportsIndirectInputEvents</key>
	<true/>
</dict>
</plist>
```

---

**One thing you must do manually:**

Find `REVERSED_CLIENT_ID` in your `GoogleService-Info.plist` — it looks like:
```
com.googleusercontent.apps.653168096175-xxxxxxxxxx